{
  "stem": "4247.2",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it resulted in salvaging a few people-- a few hundred people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They crossed the border at Romania-- and I think that's what this man did-- came through Romania and Yugoslavia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Eventually, they found their way to Palestine, as it was called at that time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that was the only organized [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] deviation from the ordinary, the meek ordinary, apart from some individual effort, which I have done later on, which I'm going to tell you about.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But that was not organized.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was a--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--individual, absolutely single effort.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] So [SIGHS] in-- so in '44, in '44, I, I, I obtained my, my certificate of being a fully fledged toolmaker.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The major event was in January.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] January 18, 1944, my poor mother had a stroke.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember I was called back from my toolmaking thing because a phone call came through.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he-- she was 49 at that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when I got home, I realized that she is stricken.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from January 1944 until, until March '44, she was in a hospital.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was a young woman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She was only 44.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this embolia, this clot which was lodged in her brain, was slowly dissolving to the extent that she regained perhaps 80% of her movements.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She regained 75% of her mental faculties.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But she was a, a, a, a sick woman.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And she came back from, from the hospital in March.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "On the 19th of March, 1944, the same, same time, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Germans occupied Hungary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "By that time-- the book I have given to you describes this area-- this era very, very well.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "By that time, the, the leaders of Hungary have realized that the Germans seem to have lost the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
